                &none             &kp N4  &kp N5  &kp N6            &kp EQUAL       &kp LEFT              &kp UP                 &kp DOWN          &kp RIGHT          &none
&kp LEFT_SHIFT  &kp LEFT_CONTROL  &kp N7  &kp N8  &kp N9            &kp MINUS       &kp HOME              &kp PG_UP              &kp PG_DN         &kp END            &kp BSLH  &kp GRAVE
                                          &kp N0  &kp LEFT_CONTROL  &kp LEFT_ALT    &none                 &trans                 &none
            >;

